.name
Spot
.author
Nico Francois 
.distribution
Shareware
.description
A FidoNet tosser/editor for all Amiga points (with WB 2.0+) Some features:
Supports new 3.0 features (newlook menus, memory pools,...); Fully
localized (OS 2.1+); Font sensitive; Keyboard shortcuts; All settings can
be easily changed from within Spot; Fast importing/exporting; Automatically
creates new areas for you, no tedious work; Special fast message base
format with only a few files per area; Optional fully transparent message
base crunching; Message list with powerful functions (e.g.  search body
text); Excellent support for multiple character sets (LATIN-1, IBM,...);
Built-in, fully asynchronous, Fido file request; ARexx port... plus much
more! Evaluation version 1.2b.  
